    				<h4>Vision:</h4> Optimal health for all persons in KwaZulu-Natal 
					<h4>Mission:</h4> To develop and implement a sustainable, coordinated, integrated and comprehensive health system at all levels, based on the Primary Health Care approach through the District Health System, to ensure universal access to health care
					<h4>Core Values</h4>
					<ul>
						<li>Trustworthiness, honesty and integrity </li>
						<li>Open communication, transparency and consultation </li>
						<li>Professionalism, accountability and commitment to excellence</li>
						<li>Loyalty and compassion </li>
						<li>Continuous learning, amenable to change and innovation </li>
					</ul>
